Strange eggs can be found in the small Dragonkin labratory hidden besides Elvarg's Lair on Crandor, on Lithkren, in the Lithkren Vault and in the Ungael Lab, which all become accessible during Dragon Slayer II quest.

When attempting to inspect the Ancient Mural during the quest, a spawn will come out of an egg and must be killed immediately.
